items.name: Rough Pebbles
items.description: A handful of tiny pebbles of rock made at a masonry station. Can be used to make various crafting materials or ground down to search for gem fragments.

items.description: A cut gem that could be used in various jewelry

items.description: A cut gem that could be used in various jewelry

items.description: A cut gem that could be used in various jewelry

items.description: A cut gem that could be used in various jewelry

items.name: Rough Cloth
items.description: A thick weave of cloth made by a tailor

items.name: Rough Textile
items.description: A textile made by a leatherworker to refine cloth

items.name: Refined Rough Cloth
items.description: A thick weave of cloth cloth embroidered with refined hemp

items.name: Rough Straw
items.description: Straw that comes from embergrain. Can be used to make textiles to refine cloth.

items.name: Rough Animal Hair
items.description: A particularly bristly hair from an animal. This could be used to make more refined cloth.

items.name: Basic Fish Oil
items.description: Oil made from fish. Can be used for making leather treatment and ink.

items.description: Can be grown into an Embergrain plant in a farming field.

items.name: Basic Wispweave Seeds
items.description: Can be grown into a Wispweave Plant in a farming field. Produces filaments used for making cloth.

items.name: Basic Chemical Catalyst
items.description: A catalyst that can be made and used by scholars to create various potions or consumables.

items.name: Basic Mushroom
items.description: A plump mushroom that looks edible and quite hearty. Probably better cooked.

items.name: Rough Glass Vial
items.description: A vial that could be filled with solvents or elixirs

items.name: Water Bucket
items.description: A bucket full of fresh water

items.name: Sugar
items.description: Sugar made from boiled sap. Could be used to cook something tasty

items.name: Basic Flower
items.description: A flower that could be grinded up to make pigment or used to make tea

items.name: Tier 1 Sugar
items.description: Sugar made from boiled sap. Could be used to cook something tasty.

items.name: Basic Berry
items.description: A juicy edible berry. Probably better cooked.

items.name: Rough Chemical Supply Pack
items.description: A package of chemical supplies made by a scholar. Can be used to provide supplies to a claim totem to add supplies to claim.

items.name: Rough Bauxite
items.description: A rare abrasive stone that can be used to make a leather treatment solution to refine leather.

items.name: Ferralith Ore Piece
items.description: A piece of rock with exposed bits of ore. Could be processed at a Smithing Station.

items.description: A pile of crushed ore. Could be processed into concentrate at by a smith.

items.name: Rough Braxite
items.description: A rare abrasive stone that can be used to make a leather treatment solution to refine leather.

items.name: Rough Stone Chunk
items.description: Can be used in construction or refined into a crafting block.

items.name: Plain Mashed Bulbs
items.description: Mashed potatoes. Tasty and filling but not overly interesting.

items.name: Basic Embergrain Dough
items.description: A dough ball made of Embergrain Flour.

items.name: Plain Raw Bulb Rolls
items.description: Uncooked onion rolls. Cook them in an oven to craft them!

items.name: Plain Bulb Rolls
items.description: Warm, toasty onion rolls.

items.description: A basic fertilizer made at a farming station. Used for fertilizing crops.

items.name: Wild Vegetable Seeds
items.description: Can be turned into white onion seeds by a farmer.

items.name: Basic Starbulb Plant
items.description: Can be husked into Starlight Onions to eat or Starlight Onion Seeds to replant.

items.name: Basic Embergrain
items.description: Embergrains which could be cooked into dough.
